ğŸ“Œ 1. Tools in CrewAI

ğŸ”¹ What Are Tools?

Tools allow agents to interact with the real world.

Examples:

* Web search
* File reader
* Database query
* Python execution
* APIs

Without tools:

* Agents can only generate text
  With tools:
* Agents can perform actions

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Why Tools Matter?

Tools enable:

* Real-time information retrieval
* Data processing
* Automation
* Reduced hallucination

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Tool Flow in CrewAI

```text
Agent â†’ Decides Tool â†’ Executes Tool â†’ Receives Output â†’ Continues Reasoning
```

