ğŸ“Œ 2. Collaboration Between Agents

CrewAI is designed for **role-based collaboration**.

Each agent:

* Has a defined role
* Has a specific goal
* Focuses on one responsibility

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Example Collaboration Flow

Scenario: AI Research Report

```text
Planner â†’ Researcher â†’ Analyst â†’ Writer â†’ Reviewer
```

* Planner breaks task
* Researcher collects info
* Analyst processes data
* Writer drafts report
* Reviewer improves quality

Each agent builds on the previous output.

