----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“Œ 6. Example Conceptual Code Structure

```python
research_agent = Agent(
    role="Researcher",
    goal="Find latest AI advancements",
    tools=[web_search_tool],
    verbose=True
)

writer_agent = Agent(
    role="Writer",
    goal="Write structured report",
    verbose=True
)

crew = Crew(
    agents=[research_agent, writer_agent],
    tasks=[research_task, writing_task],
    verbose=True
)
```

